<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> KLINGON EMPIRE

Gorkon, an accomplished general, is respected and feared by the Klingon Empire''s enemies. He is seen as a rising star in Klingon politics, and is expected to take a seat on the High Council within the decade.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
