<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> NERO''S CREW
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE

Vemet worked on the Narada for years; a friend of Nero''s and a constant voice of caution and reason, Vemet helped steer the crew through many a difficult situation. When Nero called for revenge, Vemet advised care and planning, but provided his service all the same.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2959514562, 'officer_name_16', 'Vemet', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
