INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2959514562, 'officer_ability_desc_32', '<color=#309BBF>Feel the Heat</color>
At the beginning of each round, if the opponent''s ship is <color=#FFC926>Burning</color>, Vemet decreases its Shield Health by an amount equal to <color=#40FF60>{0:0.#%}</color> of the Health of all Officers on the ship.

<color=#B8DEE5>Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship</color>.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2959514562, 'officer_ability_name_32', 'Feel the Heat', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2959514562, 'officer_ability_short_desc_32', '<color=#40FF60>{0:#,#%}</color> of total Officer Health deducted from the Shield Health of a Burning ship each round', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2959514562, 'officer_ability_desc_31', '<color=#309BBF>Romulan Tenacity</color>
If the ship survives an attack that depletes its shields and is destroyed in one of the following attacks during the same battle, the battle is lost but Vemet heals <color=#40FF60>{0:0.#%}</color> of the Hull Health and the ship survives. This takes precedence over the NSEA Protector’s Omega-13 Ship Ability and does not stack.

<color=#B8DEE5>Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship</color>.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (2959514562, 'officer_ability_name_31', 'Romulan Tenacity', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
