Kumak was the tactical officer aboard the Narada. Before the destruction of Romulus, Kumak was an expert with a mining laser, able to bore impressively precise seams into asteroids. That skill transferred over surprisingly well to shooting down Federation starships.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
