 Every time the opponent is hit by an energy weapon attack, Arix has a <color=#40FF60>{0:0.#%}</color> chance of <color=#FFC926>Burning</color> it.
<i>(Weapons with multiple shots will only trigger this maneuver once per attack.)</i>

<color=#B8DEE5>Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship</color>.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
