Krell is a member of Klingon Intelligence and specializes in counter-intelligence against Starfleet and the Federation. He''s been involved in the theft of several starship schematics, and has personally tested out the analyses of Starfleet vessel weakness; after all, theft is dishonorable, except in the name of victory for the Klingon Empire.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
