<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE

Liviana Charvanek only recently earned her command, but has distinguished herself as a clever and ruthless strategist, and a true daughter of Romulus. While she favors to strike from positions of strength, she has earned the respect of the Klingons by her ability to fight them toe to toe.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
