<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> NONE

Harry Mudd’s half-Human, half-Bajoran daughter, she grew a deep resentment towards her father after being abandoned by him at an early age. However, she couldn’t resist following in his footsteps, becoming one of the most notorious thieves and smugglers in the galaxy. 

With her eventual goal to take over her father’s operations, Ro is driven by ambition, rather than the ego and cynicism that drives Harry, and wants to build a sustainable empire beyond her father’s schemes and vanity projects.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
