INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (677303054, 'officer_flavor_text_122', '<color=#40CFFF>CLASS:</color> SCIENCE
<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> OUTLAWS
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> NONE

Harcourt Fenton Mudd. Many call him a thief, a liar, a rogue, a con-man. He is all of these things. But he is, above all, a survivor.
Arriving in our universe through a complicated series of mycellial networks, this alternate Mudd might, at first, seem similar to our own. Indeed, he is charming, quick witted and incredibly intelligent but this Mudd has one crucial differentiating factor. There is no line he will not cross.
The cruel fate he suffered at the hands of Klingon captors hardened Mudd, turning him ruthless. It showed him that there can be no room for morals in the fight for survival. This new outlook, as well as his penchant for cons and thievery, put him at odds with the crew of the USS Discovery, who have proven to be a mighty thorn in his side. Now that Mudd is here, he will do whatever it takes to make it out alive… and maybe wreak a little havoc while he’s at it.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (677303054, 'officer_name_122', 'Harcourt Fenton Mudd', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
INSERT INTO officer_translations (officer_id, key, text, modified) VALUES (677303054, 'officer_name_short_122', 'HARRY MUDD', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
