<color=#40CFFF>GROUP:</color> GLORY IN THE KILL
<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> KLINGON EMPIRE

Kras has served in advisory roles for some time now; more a scientist and negotiator than a commander, but a warrior all the same. Behind many of the rising stars in the Klingon forces, Kras has quietly imparted knowledge and experience. Koloth, Kor, and Kang all count Kras as mentor in their early career. Recently, Kras has turned his attention to Klaa and his crew.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
